All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
MTImageMapTouch
MTImageMapTouch interface delivers a selected polygon map.
MTImageMapView
MTImageMapView lets a user to select a polygon map on an image.
MTPoint
MTPoint contains a single (x,y) coordinate of 1) a polygon map or 2) a touch point in the logical space of dp unit.
MTPolygon
MTPolygon contains a polygon map made with a group of MTPoint, and can check if a point is contained.
